<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>CV Templates - C.O.A. CV BUILDER</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/dashboard.css">
</head>
<body>
    <!-- HEADER / NAVBAR -->
    <header class="dashboard-header">
        <nav class="navbar">
            <div class="nav-container">
                <div class="logo-section">
                    <img src="/images/logo.png" alt="C.O.A. TECH Logo" class="logo">
                    <h1>C.O.A. CV BUILDER</h1>
                </div>
                <div class="nav-links">
                    <a href="/">Home</a>
                    <a href="/dashboard">Dashboard</a>
                    <a href="/auth/logout" class="btn-logout">Logout</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <main class="dashboard-main">
        <div class="dashboard-container">
            <section style="margin: 3rem 0;">
                <h2 style="color: #006B3F; font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">CV Templates</h2>
                <p style="color: #4b5563; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
                    We are gradually rolling out multiple professional CV layouts. For now, all CVs use our core
                    professional template, and Premium users will get access to additional layouts as we publish them.
                </p>

                <div class="features-comparison">
                    <div class="feature-item">
                        <span class="check active">Available</span>
                        <span><strong>Professional Classic</strong> – clean, structured CV for most roles (currently in use).</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="feature-item">
                        <span class="check inactive">Coming soon</span>
                        <span><strong>Modern Corporate</strong> – a more compact layout for senior and corporate roles.</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="feature-item">
                        <span class="check inactive">Coming soon</span>
                        <span><strong>Tech / Projects</strong> – layout that highlights skills, projects, and technologies.</span>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <p style="margin-top: 1.5rem; color: #6b7280;">
                    As we add more templates, you will be able to choose which layout to use when previewing or downloading your CV.
                </p>
            </section>
        </div>
    </main>
</body>
</html>